    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Areas of partial darkness produced by a body intercepting the direct rays of the sun or other luminary, so that radiation is unable to reach the darkened area directly.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
